Golgi was preceded by an a cappella line of Back in My Hometown.
NO2 featured Fishman on vacuum.
Harpua included a narration about the comet that crashed into Jupiter. Poster got hit by a comet.
Antelope included a Simpsons signal and Trey running around the stage with a megaphone.
Catapult saw Fishman take a verbal jab at Trey and his upcoming wedding before quickly recanting.
Chalk Dust included a Barracuda tease
